{"tid":236214,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【電話輸入法】倉頡vs筆劃vs語音 邊個打中文最快最準？","createTime":"2017-05-09T14:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T03:54:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d69ceb1733f142d7eb78f9e4d6cd7254c5245bd5","tid":236214,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170509/56667428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170509%2F56667428&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2Bf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=8809586e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170509%2F56667428&h=fb724b09\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170509/56667428</a><br />\n中文輸入法有多種選擇，筆劃、倉頡、速成、廣東話拼音，還有近年十分多人喜歡用的語音輸入法，到底哪一款最好用打字最準最快手？果籽記者日打夜打，搭車用電話都要趕着打稿，最適合當人肉測試員，精挑細選後選出了三位代表人物，分別是常用「筆劃」打稿的Lorraine、ICQ年代開始用「倉頡」的Vincent和近來推崇用「語音」輸入的Ivan。<br />\n<br />\n測試文章分別是中英夾雜兼口語多多的羅家英版《Only You》和用字艱澀的佛經《般若波羅密多心經》。三個人各試盡筆劃、倉頡、速成、Google廣東話拼音和Google 及iOS的語音輸入，再取其平均成績，結果單手打字筆劃較快，雙手打字則倉頡奪冠。不過最令人意外的是Google的語音輸入，整篇《般若波羅密多心經》讀出來一隻字都沒有錯，「心無罣礙」、「涅槃」、「阿耨多羅三藐三菩提」這些高難度字眼都認得到，相反iOS就多次把「波羅」認做「菠蘿」。其實iOS的語音輸入已經不俗，但Google更強，中英夾雜也能認得準確，值得推介。"},{"pid":"b61850b5c6e0e95d07c7754764496dca9f4a2577","tid":236214,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79122e3de12180ca592edff8e5844013c80d7edb","tid":236214,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"記者識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3071788439acf56e07cd86ffd886f9a229b5a1c","tid":236214,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1695b55da86363d448f83c2ad8d6edd47a683b75","tid":236214,"uid":8153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"細moon嘅話一定筆劃好體倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好易hi錯隔離制"},{"pid":"7702da0fbe8aaac9056614d52cc782d49f01cf65","tid":236214,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T01:07:16.000Z","msg":"Google語音輸入背後有個語料庫，心經呢d咁經典既text個corpus一定有，認啱哂好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5b5c3400df9315a30803ac93efafef0da31f53","tid":236214,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53aa921a8fa954efc8d919703c4697e63697c8c3","tid":236214,"uid":1424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細moon嘅話一定筆劃好體倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好易hi錯隔離制</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2771669f0784b3262faf23666447cc03706efd94","tid":236214,"uid":99536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"on9 架咩<br />\n邊有人用單手打倉頡"},{"pid":"eada36093e504b9f01c6f9c7e6a221d5d650061f","tid":236214,"uid":47128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9 架咩<br />\n邊有人用單手打倉頡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用手機單手打倉頡有咩問題"},{"pid":"00b0326c79114e1239b72be52238fdfd35c38f90","tid":236214,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.ikea.com/ms/media/cho_room/20171/hospitality/20171_cobh03a/20171_cobh03a_01_PH138193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%